---
title: Two-Cheese Chicken & Bacon Parmigiana with Spiced Fries, Slaw & Garlic Aioli
description: Who doesn’t love a good parmigiana? Take it to new levels by adding rashers of bacon for a protein combo that sure is easy to love. Paired with crispy spiced fries and aioli, we bet it'll feel like a gourmet pub-bistro dinner tonight!
